ADDITIONAL NOTE ON DATASET:

This project uses the "Top Agriculture Crop Disease" dataset published on
Kaggle by kamal01 (https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/kamal01/top-agriculture-crop-disease).
Please review Kaggle's dataset licence terms before using the dataset for
commercial purposes.

ADDITIONAL NOTE ON MODEL WEIGHTS:

The MobileNetV2 backbone is pre-trained on ImageNet. ImageNet model weights
distributed through TensorFlow/Keras are subject to the Apache 2.0 licence.
The fine-tuned model weights produced by this project are released under MIT.

