DISCLAIMER:

This software is intended as a decision-support tool for farmers. It does not
replace professional agricultural advice. Always consult a qualified
agronomist or local agricultural extension officer before applying any
pesticide or fungicide treatment. The authors accept no liability for crop
losses or adverse outcomes arising from reliance on the app's predictions.
